column2: Giving Back Territory decisions activated
Giving back territory
By activating this decision you can check if you can give back territory to your friends. (NOTE: You need to leave and re-enter the Diplomacy tab for the interface to properly update!)
Giving back territory
By activating this decision you can hide the Give Back Territory type decisions from the interface. (NOTE: You need to leave and re-enter the Diplomacy tab for the interface to properly update!)
